WEBVTT

00:01.814 --> 00:03.281
Happiness is hard to find.

00:03.349 --> 00:06.350
We gotta try taking risks,

00:06.418 --> 00:07.979
without worrying
about the consequences.

00:09.293 --> 00:10.797
JENNA:
<i>I know</i>

00:10.865 --> 00:12.466
that I was the one
who kissed you, but...

00:12.500 --> 00:14.539
this isn't working.

00:14.609 --> 00:17.647
Your face is the saddle
Jenna's been giddyupping on?

00:17.714 --> 00:19.315
No, no, no, no, no.
It was only one kiss.

00:19.317 --> 00:21.750
Rah!
I'm taking you to get some help.

00:21.818 --> 00:23.485
Bad dog!
You stay away from me!

00:23.554 --> 00:24.556
Whoa!

00:26.226 --> 00:27.392
Dad?

00:27.460 --> 00:29.361
When your dad had me committed,

00:29.428 --> 00:30.932
I know it crushed him.

00:30.999 --> 00:32.268
He was scared

00:32.336 --> 00:34.002
that you would turn out
the same way.

00:34.070 --> 00:35.838
He was actually
trying to help us.

00:35.906 --> 00:37.375
I've been fighting so hard

00:37.443 --> 00:39.046
to save our friendship,

00:39.114 --> 00:40.634
instead of focusing
on the relationship

00:40.648 --> 00:41.849
that actually mattered:

00:41.917 --> 00:43.085
the one with my father.

00:43.153 --> 00:45.298
I'm not well when I'm with you.

